<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" xmlns:html="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id74659bb9-3a70-11f1-9d9e-dfac6d46cab7" identifier="/us/usc/t36/s20903"><num value="20903">§ 20903.</num><heading> Purposes</heading>
<chapeau style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">The purposes of the corporation are as provided in the articles of incorporation and include—</chapeau><paragraph style="-uslm-lc:I12" class="indent1" id="id74659bba-3a70-11f1-9d9e-dfac6d46cab7" identifier="/us/usc/t36/s20903/1"><num value="1">(1)</num><content> encouraging fraternity for the common good;</content>
</paragraph>
<paragraph style="-uslm-lc:I12" class="indent1" id="id74659bbb-3a70-11f1-9d9e-dfac6d46cab7" identifier="/us/usc/t36/s20903/2"><num value="2">(2)</num><content> fostering patriotism and loyalty;</content>
</paragraph>
<paragraph style="-uslm-lc:I12" class="indent1" id="id74659bbc-3a70-11f1-9d9e-dfac6d46cab7" identifier="/us/usc/t36/s20903/3"><num value="3">(3)</num><content> assisting widows and orphans of deceased ex-prisoners of war;</content>
</paragraph>
<paragraph style="-uslm-lc:I12" class="indent1" id="id74659bbd-3a70-11f1-9d9e-dfac6d46cab7" identifier="/us/usc/t36/s20903/4"><num value="4">(4)</num><content> assisting ex-prisoners of war who have been injured or disabled as a result of their service;</content>
</paragraph>
<paragraph style="-uslm-lc:I12" class="indent1" id="id74659bbe-3a70-11f1-9d9e-dfac6d46cab7" identifier="/us/usc/t36/s20903/5"><num value="5">(5)</num><content> maintaining allegiance to the United States;</content>
</paragraph>
<paragraph style="-uslm-lc:I12" class="indent1" id="id74659bbf-3a70-11f1-9d9e-dfac6d46cab7" identifier="/us/usc/t36/s20903/6"><num value="6">(6)</num><content> preserving and defending the United States from all enemies; and</content>
</paragraph>
<paragraph style="-uslm-lc:I12" class="indent1" id="id74659bc0-3a70-11f1-9d9e-dfac6d46cab7" identifier="/us/usc/t36/s20903/7"><num value="7">(7)</num><content> maintaining historical records.</content>
</paragraph>
<sourceCredit id="id74659bc1-3a70-11f1-9d9e-dfac6d46cab7">(<ref href="/us/pl/105/225">Pub. L. 105–225</ref>, <date date="1998-08-12">Aug. 12, 1998</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/112/1290">112 Stat. 1290</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
